[The Department for Environment, Food and Rural Affairs (DEFRA)
confirmed that the PDV can be fatal to dogs that have not been
inoculated:
<http://www.defra.gov.uk/wildlife-countryside/ewd/seals/pdv.htm>
A guidance note on seal vaccination can be seen at:
<http://www.defra.gov.uk/wildlife-
countryside/ewd/seals/vaccination.htm>
